quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  63,9,O believers! Do not let your wealth or your children distract you from remembrance of God. Those who do so will be the losers
  63,10,"And spend out of what We have provided you with before death comes to one of you and he says, \"My Lord! If only You would grant me respite for a little while, then I would give alms and be among the righteous"
  63,11,But God will not grant a reprieve to a soul when its appointed time has come; God is well-aware of what you do